  <summary>10/24/1995--Introduced.
Fairness in Agriculture Act - Amends the Agricultural Act of 1949 to repeal price support authority. Amends the Commodity Credit Corporation Charter Act to eliminate Commodity Credit Corporation price support authority. Amends the Agricultural Adjustment Act of 1938 to repeal acreage allotment and marketing quota provisions.</summary>
